OL,3,GOPINIONCGreen paper recognises the
OL,4,Cimportance of the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe debate on what happens next should
OL,7,Fbe a positive one ` not an existential
OL,8,Fbattle.
OL,10,FThe points for discussion include
OL,11,Fgovernance arrangements, political
OL,12,Fappointees to the board and whether the
OL,13,Fcorporation should have an actual
OL,14,Frequirement to counter misinformation
OL,15,Felsewhere.
OL,17,FSupporters of the BBC should have no
OL,18,Fdifficulty entering into this
OL,19,Fdiscussion.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
