OL,3,GOPINIONCGreen paper recognises the
OL,4,Cimportance of the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FAny organisation which is to survive
OL,7,Fneeds to be self critical.
OL,9,FWhat can the BBC do better? Are there
OL,10,Fthings it does too little or too much
OL,11,Fof?
OL,13,FHow can major errors ` like the
OL,14,Fnotorious Donald Trump edit ` be dealt
OL,15,Fwith more effectively?
OL,17,FWhat the green paper is not suggesting
OL,18,Fis a smaller BBC or one which retreats
OL,19,Ffrom popular programmes.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
