OL,3,GOPINIONCGreen paper recognises the
OL,4,Cimportance of the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FArguments about commercial funding and
OL,7,Fsubscription are being revisited. But
OL,8,Ffew within the industry think there is
OL,9,Fthe slightest chance of any existing TV
OL,10,For radio services carrying ads or going
OL,11,Fbehind a paywall.
OL,13,FThe realistic question is about whether
OL,14,Fthere is a way to address the genuine
OL,15,Fproblems with the current system.
